On June 14th, 2021, at approximately 12:40 PM, a 30-year-old male victim was standing in front of 104 West 29th St. when an unidentified individual spit in his face while making anti-Asian statements. Recognize him? DM 
@NYPDTips
 or call 1-800-577-TIPS.

On 9/29/21 at approx. 7:51 AM, at 8th Ave and 35th St in Manhattan, a male on a bicycle approached a 49-year-old female, from behind, made contact with her with his bicycle and made an anti-Asian statement. Recognize him? DM 
@NYPDTips
 or Telephone1-800-577-TIPS.
